{"lemma":"يَبِس","slug":"يَبِس","root":"#.ب.س","root_slug":"_-ب-س","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ب-س","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"يَبِس","root":"يبس","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42434","n42439","n42440","n42441","n42442"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%8A%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90%D8%B3"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become dry"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dry"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Aramaic יבש (“to be dry”) and Hebrew יָבֵשׁ (yavésh, “dry, arid”)."},"ipa":["/ja.bi.sa/","/jab.ba.sa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42434","headword_ar":"يَبِسَ","root":"ybs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yayobasu","text_ar":"يَيْبَسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAbasu","text_ar":"يَابَسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yayobisu","text_ar":"يَيْبِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) which latter is extr., (S, M, K,) so that it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yay^isa","text_ar":"يَيِسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yubosN","text_ar":"يُبْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabasN","text_ar":"يَبَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, * TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabosN","text_ar":"يَبْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yubuwsapN","text_ar":"يُبُوسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K [but not there said to be an inf. n., being only mentioned there in an explanation of the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabasN","text_ar":"يَبَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and accord. to general rule it would be an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabusa","text_ar":"يَبُسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is probably an obsolete form,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it dried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dried up; after having been moist, humid, succulent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, K:) or, [rather,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it dried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dried up:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also, [but perhaps tropically,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, stiff, rigid, tough, firm, resisting pressure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raTuba","text_ar":"رَطُبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yubosN","text_ar":"يُبْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruTuwbapN","text_ar":"رُطُوبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yubuwsapN","text_ar":"يُبُوسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quality which necessarily implies difficulty of assuming form and of becoming separated and of becoming united:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KT:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~abasa","text_ar":"اِتَّبَسَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotaEala","text_ar":"اِفْتَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) as well as [its original form]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aiytabasa","text_ar":"اِيتَبَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA [there written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Atabasa","text_ar":"اتَبَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it has the conjunction"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa","text_ar":"وَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to it]) aor. [of the former]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yat~abisu","text_ar":"يَتَّبِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of the latter]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAtabisu","text_ar":"يَاتَبِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabisa","text_ar":"يَبِسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or is quasipass. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yab~asahu","text_ar":"يَبَّسَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and therefore signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became dried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dried up;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; (Ibn-Es-Sarráj, S;) [as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tyb~s","text_ar":"تيبّس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in the TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eks","text_ar":"عكس"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabisa Aln~abaAtu","text_ar":"يَبِسَ النَّبَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage, became dry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabisati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"يَبِسَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The land lost its water and moisture; its water and moisture went away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabisato TabiyEatuhu","text_ar":"يَبِسَتْ طَبِيعَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became costive."},{"kind":"text","text":"And]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabisa","text_ar":"يَبِسَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bayonahumaA","text_ar":"مَا بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That friendship which was between them two became withered;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 2, and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"varFY","text_ar":"ثَرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":";) i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they became disunited, each from the other; the bond of friendship that united them, each to the other, became severed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaATaEaA","text_ar":"تَقَاطَعَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) ―         -b3-  Hence also, (M,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aiybaso","text_ar":"اِيبَسْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in a copy of the M [agreeably with an explanation of its part. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAbisN","text_ar":"يَابِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., and in a copy of the A written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ayobaso","text_ar":"ايْبَسْ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayobiso","text_ar":"اَيْبِسْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayobasa","text_ar":"اَيْبَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akorimo","text_ar":"اَكْرِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be thou silent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cease thou from speaking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, K:) said to a man. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","TA","KT"]},{"entry_id":"n42439","headword_ar":"يَبْسٌ","root":"ybs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1:       -A2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAbisN","text_ar":"يَابِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n42440","headword_ar":"يُبْسٌ","root":"ybs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1:       -A2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAbisN","text_ar":"يَابِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n42441","headword_ar":"يَبَسٌ","root":"ybs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1:       -A2-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAbisN","text_ar":"يَابِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n42442","headword_ar":"يَبِسٌ","root":"ybs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAbisN","text_ar":"يَابِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}